title: Kim Lenz and The Jaguars - Follow Me 2013
description:
L.A. Rockabilly Queen Kim Lenz returns with her fourth studio album, Follow Me - her first album since the 2009's acclaimed It's All True. Follow Me continues the passionate driving sound that built Lenz's reputation. As one of the modern roots rockin' scene's pre-eminent singer-songwriters, Follow Me takes Lenz's music in a more intimate direction. Produced by Carl Sonny Leyland, and featuring Big Sandy guitarist Ashley Kingman. Kim Lenz penned many of the tracks on Follow Me herself. This is Kim Lenz like you've never heard her before! (raucousrecords.com)
